{"tid":469508,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳工人被下降電梯壓著重傷","createTime":"2017-11-15T11:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T11:28:54.000Z","uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0b8ac6656cf98acfb1e4be000eb4673c37bcbb57","tid":469508,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:25:58.000Z","msg":"將軍澳景林邨發生工業意外，一名工人被升降機壓著，由消防員救出時重傷昏迷，在深切治療部留醫，情況危殆。 <br />\n<br />\n六十二歲姓李的工人，在將軍澳醫院急救後，由醫護人員陪同，由救護車轉送往伊利沙伯醫院。意外發生在上午約十時，出事升降機暫時封鎖，現場消息指，事主在景棉樓地下大堂，把升降機升起後，俯身靠向機槽進行測檢，升至三樓的升降機突然下墮跌，一度把他壓在機槽，大廈保安報警，消防員到場把事主救出送院，勞工處派人調查事故原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/516285/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F516285%2F&d=ldFL%2FGoPYvM%2FPjc8ZZXggPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=521a9234\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F516285%2F&h=7d516ed1\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/516285/</a>"},{"pid":"61a196cf794253391b71f03e105adb83feeaa5a4","tid":469508,"uid":13408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:28:54.000Z","msg":"六張野都可以做勞動人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}